# [color=DaBlue] **The Mad Wizard**[/color]

**Neutral Killer**

*Studious-Passive*
You are never in your room when you need to be killed, you are always studying (Night Immunity)
NOTES:
I personally think he never grew out of his learning



*Day Ability 1-Dark Chant*
You will chant some dark magic, making your next target show up as their Unseen/Cult class-2 uses

*Night Ability 1-Chain Lightning*
You will zap somebody tonight, killing them and the person they visit.-Infinite uses 

*Night Ability 2-Fire Ward*
You will burn somebodies room, killing them and anybody who visits them along with getting rid of their logs- 3 uses

*You win when you kill everybody, except those who need to survive*

*Lore*
After the new king&#39;s crowning, the Court Wizard began to argue with the new king, one agruement result in the old man being thrown into the dungeon. The wizard was locked in the dungeon for 5 weeks. They got food and water every other day. The wizard was let go after the princess&#39;s begging. After this, the wizard began to distance himself from the royals and the people and started to use his good powers for evil. A few years later, the king asked them to help him to crush some rebels in his court. Seeing this as his chance to get revenge, he gladly agreed to go to the court, and of course, execute his revenge

CHANGELOG:
10/13-Added Calming Spell and Dark Chant
10/14-Changed Calming Spell to have Night immunity
10/14-Nixed Madness and replaced wit Studious, Killed Calming spell,, Made Zapz! kill the person they visit that night
10/15-Renamed zapz! to Chain Lightning
10/18-Removed Occupy immunity
1/26/18-Made fire ward also destroy their victiems logs</description>
    
